      <textAnnotation id="sid-7F454FC2-6551-4910-9DE7-42A3940FFF49" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Advanced Shipping Notification (ASN) sent from External Vendor</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-54E367B4-6B7E-4C03-9201-628162019E2C" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Assignment of the batch characteristics to newly created SAP batch via ASN process need to be discussed with LE team</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-8DFA9615-C452-451A-8905-053CBD098E6B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP Batch with Expiration date and Manufacturing Date from Vendor batch will use SAP Internal Number Range</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-585D951F-FC67-4115-9573-053AB2CF3A50" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Vendor Batch will be stored in Vendor Batch Field on Batch Master</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F5A6ADB7-A32E-429D-AB57-E3A19913E994" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/99ed2fb6879346238999fda867d77df1</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel ref="text_name" valign="middle" x="53.0" y="74.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP Extended Warehouse 
Management (EWM)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-4BF49AFB-1E8B-4FF0-A7A5-055E08B27B70" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>(GR Label Upon Good Receipt With Batch Number)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-A5BDB47E-2C4A-4ABB-B4EC-9EE1E17A2CD4" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Inbound Delivery created manually for Non ASN Scenario</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3C6E9407-B68E-47AF-A892-E180004C901D" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-964BC8A6-E9C7-45B0-827F-71773B2CD799" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Inbound Delivery created via Batch Job for Non ASN Scenario</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F51911E3-9213-45E3-9A58-3868349E27A6" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: Procure to Pay (PTP)
Process Group: L Logistics &amp; Inventory Management
Process Name: L-040-090 Assign Batch Tracking Number</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7FA778FE-AA21-4991-9CDB-483261992543" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow is Applicable to R3: 
Receiving from External Vendor Scenario :ASN and Non ASN Scenario 
Applicable Parts - Spares 
Intel Owned Inventory ,Supplier Consignment and Copper Shipments</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-93514669-3B2C-4FF1-B8EE-046A9856001F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Johnson, Graeme &lt;graeme.johnson@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
